-- INSTANT VIEW: FOMC cuts target rate to 1 pct
-- 
-- Wed Oct 29, 2008 8:20pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/10/30/us-usa-markets-fomc-view-idUSTRE49S81320081030

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - The U.S. Federal Reserve cut a key interest rate by a hefty half-percentage point on Wednesday to prevent a widening credit crisis from tipping the United States into a deep and prolonged recession. 

